    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3, a flagship of mechanical purity. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally impeccable, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a completely original suspension geometry. Maintained to a rigorous standard, the compression across all cylinders remains within factory tolerances, and the rod bearing service has been preemptively addressed. A truly turnkey specimen for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
